  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How do I contact Handy customer service?",
  "response": "To contact Handy customer service, you have several options available:\n\n### 1. **Help Center (Website)**\nHandy\u2019s Help Center is a comprehensive resource where you can find answers to common questions and submit support requests.\n\n- **Visit the Help Center:** [Handy Help Center](https://www.handy.com/help)\n- **Browse Topics:** Navigate through various categories to find solutions related to your issue.\n- **Submit a Request:** If you can\u2019t find the answer you need, you can submit a support ticket through the Help Center.\n\n### 2. **In-App Support**\nIf you\u2019re using the Handy mobile app, you can access support directly within the app.\n\n- **Open the Handy App:** Ensure you\u2019re logged into your account.\n- **Navigate to Support:** Typically found in the menu or settings section.\n- **Submit a Request or Chat:** Follow the prompts to either send a message or start a live chat with a support representative.\n\n### 3. **Email Support**\nYou can reach out to Handy\u2019s support team via email for assistance.\n\n- **Email Address:** support@handy.com\n- **Provide Details:** When emailing, include relevant information such as your account details, a description of the issue, and any relevant order or booking numbers to help expedite the process.\n\n### 4. **Social Media**\nHandy is active on various social media platforms where you can send messages or find additional support resources.\n\n- **Twitter:** [@handy](https://twitter.com/handy)\n- **Facebook:** [Handy on Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/handy)\n  \nSending a direct message or mentioning them in a post can sometimes result in a quicker response.\n\n### 5. **Phone Support**\nAs of my knowledge cutoff in April 2023, Handy primarily focuses on digital support channels. They may not offer direct phone support to customers. However, you can check their Help Center or official website for any updates or additional contact methods that may have been introduced.\n\n### 6. **FAQ Section**\nBefore reaching out, you might find answers to your questions in Handy\u2019s Frequently Asked Questions section.\n\n- **Access FAQs:** [Handy FAQs](https://www.handy.com/help/faq)\n\n### Tips for Effective Support:\n- **Be Clear and Concise:** Clearly describe your issue, including any relevant details like booking numbers, dates, and the names of Handy professionals involved.\n- **Check Spam Folder:** If you\u2019re expecting a reply via email, ensure to check your spam or junk folder in case the response was misrouted.\n- **Provide Contact Information:** Make sure your contact details are up-to-date so that the support team can reach you easily.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date contact information, always refer to [Handy\u2019s official website](https://www.handy.com/) or the latest version of their mobile app.",
